Smart is the woman that whips out a wallet to pay the metaphoric piper promptly instead of rummaging without a clue in the dark recesses of her voluminous handbag at crucial moments. Wallets are convenient when you need to quickly run down to the grocery store because picking out a bag in the spur of that moment will only be tedious. The American Swan West Palm Wallet - For Women simplifies things and lets you carry around bare essentials without much hoopla.

Made for the woman who favors practicality over finery the wallet is perfect for catching up over a quick cup of coffee when you do not want to be burdened by a big ballooning bag. With leather on the outside and canvas on the inside the wallet is both sturdy and stylish without compromising on functionality. If you are the type that does not like the tedium of carrying around a bag in your hands this wallet is the perfect solution; the bi-fold wallet fits right into your pocket while not crumpling your crisp notes of money. Store your cash and cards in the multiple section holder and snap the metal closure shut with an attitude that will blow everyone's minds.
